OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Results across
OL,4,CSouth West as thousands take to the
OL,5,Cpolls
OL,7,FIt's local elections results day and
OL,8,Fthousands of residents in the West
OL,9,FCountry took to the polls yesterday to
OL,10,Fcast their vote.
OL,12,FIn the South West, voters elected
OL,13,Fcouncillors in four council areas.
OL,14,FThey were Swindon, Cheltenham, Exeter
OL,15,Fand Plymouth.
OL,17,FIn both Plymouth and Exeter, people
OL,18,Fwere voting to elect a third of each
OL,19,Fcouncil. Whereas in Cheltenham, it's
OL,20,Fhalf of the council and in Swindon the
OL,21,Fentirety of the council.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
