OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Results across
OL,4,CSouth West as thousands take to the
OL,5,Cpolls
OL,7,FResults are expected to offer an early
OL,8,Fsnapshot of the public mood on key
OL,9,Fpolitical issues.
OL,11,FIn Exeter, Labour have lost overall
OL,12,Fcontrol of the council after being in
OL,13,Fpower for 14 years.
OL,15,FWhile the party remains the largest
OL,16,Fgroup at the authority, it lost five
OL,17,Fof the fourteen seats that were being
OL,18,Fcontested there. That takes the
OL,19,Fparties overall seat number down to 18
OL,20,F- two below the majority mark.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
