OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Results across
OL,4,CSouth West as thousands take to the
OL,5,Cpolls
OL,7,FThe Green Party is now the second
OL,8,Flargest group after making three
OL,9,Fgains, taking their total number of
OL,10,Fseats to ten.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Liberal Democrats gained
OL,13,Fone seat to move to five seats and
OL,14,FReform UK made a gain of two compared
OL,15,Fto 2022.
OL,17,FIn Plymouth, despite Labour
OL,18,Fmaintaining overall control of the
OL,19,Fcouncil due to the number of seats
OL,20,Fbeing contested, it was a night of
OL,21,Fhuge losses.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
