OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Results across
OL,4,CSouth West as thousands take to the
OL,5,Cpolls
OL,7,FThe party ended the count with nine
OL,8,Ffewer councillors compared to the last
OL,9,Ftime the seats were contested in 2022.
OL,10,FIt remains the majority party by five
OL,11,Fseats.
OL,13,FFor Reform UK though, it was a
OL,14,Fcompletely different story. The party
OL,15,Fsaw huge gains taking 14 of the 19
OL,16,Fseats being contested.
OL,18,FBefore tonight, Reform had never had a
OL,19,Fcouncillor elected in Plymouth.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
