OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Results across
OL,4,CSouth West as thousands take to the
OL,5,Cpolls
OL,7,FThe Conservatives have ended the night
OL,8,Fwith three councillors after loosing
OL,9,Fsix seats. Meanwhile, The Green Party
OL,10,Fgained one seat taking their total to
OL,11,Fthree councillors.
OL,13,FThe Independent group had no change
OL,14,Ffrom 2022, ending the night with four
OL,15,Fmembers.
OL,17,FAll 57 council seats on Swindon
OL,18,FBorough Council are being contested.
OL,19,FIt is the first time since 2012 that
OL,20,Fall seats have been decided in a
OL,21,Fsingle election.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
