OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Results across
OL,4,CSouth West as thousands take to the
OL,5,Cpolls
OL,7,FThose who win the ballot will help to
OL,8,Frun the authority for the next four
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FLabour currently has a 25-seat
OL,12,Fmajority at Swindon Borough Council
OL,13,Fand controls more than 40 wards.
OL,15,FThe results are expected to be
OL,16,Fannounced this evening.
OL,18,FHalf of Cheltenham Borough Council's
OL,19,Fseats are being contested.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
