OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Results across
OL,4,CSouth West as thousands take to the
OL,5,Cpolls
OL,7,FThe authority is made up of 40
OL,8,Fcouncillors, with two representing
OL,9,Feach of the borough's 20 wards.
OL,11,FHalf-out elections are held bi-
OL,12,Fannually, where residents vote for 20
OL,13,Fseats - one for each ward.
OL,15,FCurrently, the Liberal Democrats have
OL,16,Fcontrol of the council with 36 seats.
OL,17,FThe Greens have three councillors and
OL,18,Fthe People Against Bureacracy have one
OL,19,Fcouncillor.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
